WEBVTT

00:14:28.720 --> 00:14:32.616
I've thought a lot
about what I'm going to say to her

00:14:32.640 --> 00:14:33.880
when she's older.

00:14:36.400 --> 00:14:37.600
"Cady,

00:14:38.760 --> 00:14:41.976
engaging in the full
range of experience --

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:43.696
living and dying,

00:14:43.720 --> 00:14:45.200
love and loss --

00:14:46.040 --> 00:14:47.320
is what we get to do.

00:14:49.080 --> 00:14:54.120
Being human doesn't happen
despite suffering.

00:14:55.680 --> 00:14:56.960
It happens within it.

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:00.680
When we approach suffering together,